1) Download mongodb https://www.mongodb.org/downloads#production
2) Unarchive tar/zip
3) Append to PATH system variable location of ${MONGO_HOME}/bin
4) Create mkdir /data/db where locate your db(usually Mongodb/data/db)
5) Write value of mongo.data.db.path  /data/db in app.properties
6) Start server mongod --dbpath ..data/
7) Run method dataBaseManager.restoreDataBaseFromDump() to restore db from dump